<p>Retrieves the <link xref="Clutter.Action">Clutter.Action</link> with the given name in the list
of actions applied to @self</p><p>name, or None. The returned <link xref="Clutter.Action">Clutter.Action</link> is owned by the
actor and it should not be unreferenced directly</p>

